race.comment: Open race. ROCKABILLY (4) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in both starts to date before being tipped out for time to furnish. Revved up for this with a recent trial placing and can go very close to shedding the maiden tag. DEFIANT MISS (6) just missed the frame over this track and trip on debut and will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience. Can improve enough to take this out. ICYMISS (8) has been thereabouts in both career outings and gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim. Include in calculations. SHAQUE D'AMOUR (15) will be ready to peak now fourth run back and looks a must for the multiples. SECRET ROSE (9) best of the rest.
